{"tid":2137950,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"颱風「哈格比」將直撲長江流域","createTime":"2020-08-03T09:46:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T12:50:11.000Z","uid":284699,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9d613da5785e27b2d36abc2348d102c1983c55fd","tid":2137950,"uid":284699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T09:46:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2713458/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2713458%2F&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2Fx9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=c0f96a3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2713458/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2710000/2713458/200803_typhoon_00_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2710000%2F2713458%2F200803_typhoon_00_1024.jpg&h=9d7a8930&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國長江流域稍早前受連場暴雨影響，水位急劇上升，如今或再受颱風「哈格比」吹襲的威脅。據中國中央氣象台預測，颱風「哈格比」將於今日（3 日）開始逐漸靠近中國，並於浙江南部至福建北部沿海登陸，並預計明天（4 日）直逼長江流域一帶。<br />\n<br />\n..........因此中國國家防汛抗旱總指揮部，已經發出颱風警報，以及防汛防颱風 Ⅳ 級應急響應，全力監測長江各區段水位變化。"},{"pid":"0cb3df7e50a7c6be7a63c6f663ee4197c8cd1aa7","tid":2137950,"uid":25260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T09:46:42.000Z","msg":"沒事儿沒事儿"},{"pid":"a0e4ae5e5fd8149363c229c090ecdac4b6ca74ad","tid":2137950,"uid":129658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T09:46:44.000Z","msg":"中國又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c97bedb733ebbf6d80d24f7cfc4cd6032ed2855","tid":2137950,"uid":224561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T09:48:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uno2zqP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.